    questionVideo: {fileID: 32900000, guid: f4e4ae1a234dc54438399f7a52870762, type: 3}
    optionStartTime: 0
  - questionText: 10. Who was summoned to teach the children and why?
    option1: Dubledore, because he was an expert in maya tactics
    option2: Vishnu Sharma, because he was an expert in maya tactics.
    option3: Rajinikanth, because he was an expert in niti shastra
    option4: Vishnu Sharma, because he was an expert in niti shastra.
    option1IsCorrect: 0
